cs.SE, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY. 

This paper deals with software evolution and natural language processing, which are both relevant to the software engineering (cs.SE) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of Neural Machine Translation (NMT) also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves text classification and filtering, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
